{"lemma":"مُطْرِقُو","slug":"مُطْرِقُو","root":"ط.ر.ق","root_slug":"ط-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26676","n26677"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B7%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%82%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26676","headword_ar":"مُطْرِقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having a natural laxness of the eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the eyelids, and a consequent lowering of the eye towards the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bending down the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowering the eyes, looking towards the ground;"},{"kind":"text","text":"either naturally or otherwise: (see its verb, 4:)] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping silence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tir~iyqN","text_ar":"طِرِّيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  It is also applied as an epithet to a stallion-camel: and to a [she-camel such as is termed]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAliy~ap","text_ar":"جُمَالِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. one resembling a he-camel in greatness of make], and, thus applied, [and app. likewise when applied to a stallion-camel,] it may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That does not utter a grumbling cry, nor vociferate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to Khálid Ibn-Jembeh, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick in pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for he says that] it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaroqN","text_ar":"طَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ quickness of going. ” (Sh, TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miToraAqN","text_ar":"مِطْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence. ―         -b4-  And, applied to a man, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Low, ignoble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in race,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parentage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the grounds of pretension to respect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An enemy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aToraqa fulaAnN lifulaAnK","text_ar":"اَطْرَقَ فُلَانٌ لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. above [see 4, last sentence]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n26677","headword_ar":"مِطْرَقٌ","root":"Trq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}